Package: kettle
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: python-kettle-doc
Description: Configuration Management for Desktops (Python 3)
 Kettle is a configuration management program (similar to Ansible) for 
 desktop machines. Rather than focusing on remote configuration deployment,
 it handles desktop-style use cases, like restoring a system after reinstalling
 an operating system.
 .
 This package installs Kettle.

